description:
“This game is BANANAS!” — IGN
“This game makes me want to keep trying over and over and over again.” — Jacksepticeye
“This might be the weirdest game I've ever played but I'M GLAD I DID!!” — Markiplier

In this game, you play as a cat that has been trapped in another dimension.
Find your way out or stay there forever!

Features:
• Boss fights! Real Bullet Hell!
• Free your future partners and they'll help you fight evil!
• Compare the results of your run with other players on the leaderboard
• The levels are tougher than they seem at first glance. They also appear in a random sequence!
• Various skins for your cat :3
name: PUSS!
